      <title>亚马逊 Prime 用户在部分市场可免费享用 Just Eat Takeout</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/amazon-prime-users-get-fee-free-just-eat-takeout-in-some-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了扩大消费者群体，荷兰食品配送公司 Amazon.com Inc. 的 Prime 会员可以通过 Just Eat Takeaway.com 在德国、奥地利和西班牙订购外卖，且无需支付配送费。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/amazon-prime-users-get-fee-free-just-eat-takeout-in-some-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华为、腾讯即将达成协议，将微信排除在收入分成之外</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/huawei-tencent-near-deal-to-exclude-wechat-from-revenue-sharing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华为技术有限公司即将达成协议，允许腾讯控股有限公司的超级应用微信在其 Harmony 移动平台上全面运行，而不会分享任何收入，这一让步旨在捍卫其在中国相对于苹果公司新取得的领先地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/huawei-tencent-near-deal-to-exclude-wechat-from-revenue-sharing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 05:16:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国金融科技公司 Zilch 与德意志银行合作筹集 1 亿英镑债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/uk-fintech-zilch-taps-deutsche-bank-to-raise-100-million-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国金融科技公司 Zilch Technology Ltd. 在德意志银行安排的一项证券化债务融资交易中筹集了 1 亿英镑（1.27 亿美元），这家“先买后付”的公司希望在明年计划的首次公开募股之前实现扩张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/uk-fintech-zilch-taps-deutsche-bank-to-raise-100-million-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷豹路虎将恢复 Freelander 的中国产电动车版</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/jaguar-land-rover-to-revive-freelander-as-a-made-in-china-ev</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在停止生产 Freelander 十年后，捷豹路虎汽车有限公司 (Jaguar Land Rover Automotive Plc) 重新推出了这款四轮驱动汽车，并将其作为电动汽车在中国生产和销售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/jaguar-land-rover-to-revive-freelander-as-a-made-in-china-ev</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 03:37:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
