    <item>
      <title>LendingTree 表示正在调查与 Snowflake 相关的可能数据泄露事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/lendingtree-says-it-s-probing-potential-snowflake-related-data-breach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在线借贷平台 LendingTree Inc. 正在调查其是否是针对云数据分析公司 Snowflake Inc. 客户的更大规模黑客攻击的受害者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/lendingtree-says-it-s-probing-potential-snowflake-related-data-breach</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 21:27:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>洛杉矶学校禁止学生使用手机，理由是影响注意力和健康</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/la-schools-ban-cellphones-citing-distractions-and-mental-health</link>
      <description><![CDATA[洛杉矶联合学区批准全天禁止使用手机，称手机分散孩子的学习注意力、损害孩​​子的心理健康并阻碍人际关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/la-schools-ban-cellphones-citing-distractions-and-mental-health</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 20:48:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
